---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">AI Builder Blog</p>
  <h1>Building at the edge of AI, energy, and technology.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    Long-form writing on AI systems, software development, energy technology,
    and what it means to build in an era of rapid change.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-tags">
    <span class="tag">AI</span>
    <span class="tag">Energy</span>
    <span class="tag">Software</span>
    <span class="tag">Future Tech</span>
    <span class="tag">Programming</span>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
  <p class="section-label">Recent Writing</p>
  <div class="post-grid">
    {% for post in collections.posts | limit(6) %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card">
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</time>
          {% if post.data.tags %}
            {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
              {% if tag != "posts" %}
                <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <div class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.content | excerpt(40) }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="post-card-footer">Read &rarr;</div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% if collections.posts.length > 6 %}
    <p style="text-align:center; margin-top: 1rem;">
      <a href="/blog/" style="color: var(--accent-hi); font-weight: 600;">View all posts &rarr;</a>
    </p>
  {% endif %}

{% else %}
  <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2rem;">Posts coming soon.</p>
{% endif %}

<section id="about" style="margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); max-width: 640px;">
  <p class="section-label">About</p>
  <p style="color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8;">
    AI Builder Blog is a space for long-form thinking about artificial intelligence,
    software engineering, energy systems, and the evolving craft of building technology.
    Written by a builder, for builders.
  </p>
</section>
